projectElectus

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • projectElectus.Platform
      • projectElectus.Entity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Locatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Character, Enemy, Explosion, Projectile

    public class Entity
extends Platform
    This class creates and manages any entities in the game. Enemies and the Character are entities.
